  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a collection of indie games developed entirely by me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It currently includes three games, and I plan to gradually add more over time as development continues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you enter the game, you can choose a mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mission 3 : 100-Lane Crossing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497230/extras/8a6c976a13699629ac3319140b02f468.avif?t=1767145926\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mission 2 : Use an RPG to eliminate all 12 Manyfang eggs and the 12 small Manyfangs that hatch from them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497230/extras/143bc5bbace86b92047d1b1cde1be073.avif?t=1767145926\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mission 1 : Eliminate \"Manyfang\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497230/extras/ad572a892b6601b9ac69e90e71bb84cd.avif?t=1767145926\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select a mission and let the fun begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game may contain content that is not suitable for all ages or may not be appropriate for viewing in a workplace: frequent violence or bloodshed, general adult content.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a collection of indie games developed entirely by me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It currently includes three games, and I plan to gradually add more over time as development continues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you enter the game, you can choose a mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mission 3 : 100-Lane Crossing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497230/extras/8a6c976a13699629ac3319140b02f468.avif?t=1767145926\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mission 2 : Use an RPG to eliminate all 12 Manyfang eggs and the 12 small Manyfangs that hatch from them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497230/extras/143bc5bbace86b92047d1b1cde1be073.avif?t=1767145926\" width=960 height=540 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mission 1 : Eliminate \"Manyfang\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497230/extras/ad572a892b6601b9ac69e90e71bb84cd.avif?t=1767145926\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select a mission and let the fun begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game may contain content that is not suitable for all ages or may not be appropriate for viewing in a workplace: frequent violence or bloodshed, general adult content.</p>",
